OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of teenage boy on e-bike
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a 15-year-old boy on an e-bike
OL,8,Fdied in a crash.
OL,10,FDevon Simmonds died at the scene after
OL,11,Femergency services were called to the
OL,12,Fincident between the car and e-bike in
OL,13,FMiddleton, Greater Manchester, shortly
OL,14,Fbefore midday on 22 July.
OL,16,FTerrence King, 59, has now been
OL,17,Fcharged with murder and remanded in
OL,18,Fcustody after an appearance at
OL,19,FManchester Magistrates Court.
