OL,6,FFloral tributes, along with
OL,7,Fhandwritten cards, pictures and
OL,8,Fballoons have since been left at the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FDozens of youths were also seen
OL,12,Fgathered at the precinct on Tuesday
OL,13,Fevening, with fireworks let off in
OL,14,FDevon's memory and tributes scrawled
OL,15,Fon walls in graffiti.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,18,Fofficers are also conducting a wider
OL,19,Finvestigation around allegations of a
OL,20,Ftheft in events leading up to the
OL,21,Fcollision.
