OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy previously arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of theft has been bailed
OL,8,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Andrew Naismith,
OL,11,Ffrom GMP's Major Incident Team, said:
OL,12,F"This investigation is already moving
OL,13,Fat considerable pace and we have now
OL,14,Fsecured a murder charge as part of our
OL,15,Fwork.
OL,17,F"There is still much to do, and our
OL,18,Fofficers are carefully combing through
OL,19,Fall available evidence to build a
OL,20,Fpicture of the events of that day.
