OL,6,F"I am aware of footage of the incident
OL,7,Fcirculating online, and I would ask
OL,8,Fpeople to not share this footage due
OL,9,Fto ongoing proceedings, and out of
OL,10,Frespect for the boy's family, who I
OL,11,Fwould remind people are grieving at
OL,12,Fthis time."
OL,14,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,15,Fget in touch with GMP through their
OL,16,Fportal, or by ringing the
OL,17,Finvestigation team on 0161 856 1995,
OL,18,Fquoting log number 1364 of 22/07/2025.
